title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your talents are uniquely suited for your goals and ambitions. However, you may be overly self-critical if youre not where you wish to be now. You might even spin into comparing how someone elses life looks to yours. Nevertheless, all that glitters isnt gold. Keep the faith that your dreams operate on a schedule not completely within your control. Allowing progress to occur naturally might be your biggest hurdle. Originality is the source of your success. Philosopher Jean Vanier wrote, Envy comes from people's ignorance of, or lack of belief in, their own gifts. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
